New Records: Victor Wembanyama joined Hakeem Olajuwon and Andrei Kirilenko as the only NBA players to achieve a 5x5 more than once.
Key Match Events: Victor Wembanyama amassed 25 points, nine rebounds, seven assists, five blocks, and five steals.
Chris Paul contributed 19 points, 10 assists, seven rebounds, and two steals for San Antonio.
Collin Sexton put up a team-high 16 points for Utah.
